+## Championship Pick page and on-chain caveat
+
+Files:
+
+- src/pages/championship-pick/ChampionshipPick.tsx
+- src/pages/championship-pick/championship-pick.css
+- src/pages/championship-pick/index.tsx
+- src/pages/index.tsx
